info.description:
API Documentation for the [Sempo Platform](https://github.com/teamsempo/SempoBlockchain).

For local testing, run the `quick_setup_script.sh` and set the `AUTH_TOKEN` and `HOST` parameters. Alternatively, you can play with a production version of the platform on dev.withsempo.com.

NOTE: Not all APIs are currently documented


**Environment Variables**

`AUTH_TOKEN` = {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

`HOST` = {{HOST}}

